keyFacts: The document is a technical label for a Western Digital 500GB hard drive (model WD5003ABYX, serial WMAYP6107485).
The drive was manufactured on May 26, 2013, and is a product of Malaysia.
This document (EFTA00002516) is included in the Epstein case files, indicating the drive was likely seized or examined as part of the investigation.
